These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  dancer, social-worker, videographer, firefighter, paramedic, doctor, accountant
1. the paramedic is between the videographer and the social-worker##2
2. the doctor is on the right of the dancer##1
3. the accountant is on the right of the firefighter##1
4. the doctor is in the middle##1
5. the social-worker is in an odd position##4
6. the videographer is on the left of the paramedic##1
7. the dancer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3     |    4    |   5    |    6     |    7     |
| Job   | firefighter | accountant | dancer | doctor | videographer | paramedic | social-worker |

