.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: indian, french, polish, turkish, spanish, egyptian, japanese
1. the turkish is on the left of the polish##1
2. the spanish is on the far left##1
3. the french is on the right of the egyptian##1
4. the polish is in an even position##4
5. the spanish is on the left of the indian##1
6. the egyptian is on the left or right of the indian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2     |   3    |    4     |    5    |  6   |     7      |
| Nationality   | spanish | indian | egyptian | french | turkish | polish | japanese |

