.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-4::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: apricot, lilac, lavender, coral, blood-red, black, brown
1. the person who likes apricot is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
3. the person who likes lavender is in an even position##4
4. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
5. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
6. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
7. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
8. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3     |    4     |   5    |     6      |  7   |
| Color   | apricot | brown | coral | black | blood-red | lavender | lilac |

