.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-5::.
7 different pets are kept: rabbit, dog, goldfish, ferret, goat, horse, bird
1. the owner of the goldfish is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |    3    |    4     |   5   |   6   |   7    |
| Pet   | dog | ferret | goat | goldfish | rabbit | bird | horse |

