1. the fan of hip-hop is in the middle##1
2. the fan of pop is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
4. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of soul##1
5. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
6. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
7. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
8. the fan of pop is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2       |     3      |     4      |    5    |     6      |     7      |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | electronic | jazz | hip-hop | metal | soul | pop |

