.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: skateboarding, swimming, cricket, snowboarding, handball, rowing, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 4. the person who's sport is handball is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
 6. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
 8. the person who's sport is rowing is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
10. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |  2   |  3   |  4   |     5      |     6     |  7   |
| Sport   | swimming | skateboarding | weightlifting | snowboarding | handball | cricket | rowing |

 